name: Trainerkeeper
tagline: A custom CRM for fitness professionals to keep track of classes, clients, and individual progress
body:
### Thanks for using TrainerKeeper.
This project is a continual work in progress, and feedback from users like you is how we decide to prioritize what comes next.

We'd love to hear from you. [Drop us a line and let us know what you think.] (chsmike.forecast@gmail.com)
